/*
 * =============================================================================
 *  EV BIKE COMBINED DASHBOARD: DALY BMS (BLE) + GNSS (UART) -> WiFi AP
 * =============================================================================
 *
 *  HARDWARE SETUP:
 *    - ESP32-C3 Dev Module
 *    - GNSS Module: TXD -> GPIO4 | RXD -> GPIO5 | VCC -> 3V3 | GND -> GND
 *    - DALY BMS: Active and broadcasting via Bluetooth
 *
 *  SOFTWARE SETUP:
 *    - Board: ESP32C3 Dev Module
 *    - Tools -> USB CDC On Boot -> Enabled
 *    - Tools -> Partition Scheme -> Huge APP (Required for BLE + WiFi)
 *    - Libraries: NimBLE-Arduino (>= 1.4.x), TinyGPSPlus
 *
 *  USAGE:
 *    1. Connect phone to WiFi "EVBIKE-01" (Pass: evbike1234)
 *    2. Open http://192.168.4.1 (or http://evbike.local)
 * =============================================================================
 */

